江敏華。2012。〈客贛方言的魚虞有別〉[The distinctions between Yu 魚 and Yu 虞 in Hakka and Gan]。《贛方言研究（第二輯）─ 2009南昌贛方言國際學術研討會論文集》[Studies on Gan Dialects, vol. 2－Collected Papers of the 2009 International Conference on Gan Dialects] 191-203。Ed. by 胡松柏，Beijing: China Social Sciences Press。
江敏華。2011。〈從分群觀點看東部贛語與客家話的關係〉[Research on the relationships between Eastern Gan and Hakka dialects from the viewpoint of subgrouping]。《中國方言中的語言學與文化意蘊》[Chinese Dialects: Implications for Linguistics and Culture] 336-364。Ed. by Ik Sang Eom 嚴翼相，Seoul: Hanguk Munhwasa。
江敏華。2010。〈南投國姓鄉客語的語言接觸現象〉[The language contact phenomena of Hakka in Guoxing Township of Nantou]。《客語千秋─第八屆國際客方言學術研討會論文集》[The Everlasting Hakka－Collected Papers of the 8th International Conference on Hakka Dialects] 524-536。Ed. by 羅肇錦、陳秀琪，Taipei: the Crane。
江敏華。2007。〈台灣客語語言典藏的現況與資源整合─從學術研究角度看客語語言典藏的未來展望〉[The current situation and resource integration of language archives in Taiwan Hakka－on the future prospects of language archives in Hakka from academic perspective]。《語言政策的多元文化思考─「語言、社會與文化」系列叢書之二》[Multicultural Thinking on Language Policy－Book Series of Language, Society, and Culture, Part II] 387-391。Ed. by Chin-Chuan Cheng et al，Taipei: Institute of Linguistics, Academia Sinica (In Chinese)。
